Out of such things came the Oceanographic Tower 
and many, many things of that kind. And Dr. LaFond,

24:14.003 --> 24:25.037
Bob Dietz, Bob Dill, Ed Hamilton, many, many more 
deserve all kinds of credit. for the good use and

24:25.473 --> 24:29.739
imaginative use to which they put that work. I'm 
very proud of the program that the Bureau of Ships

